configure local AI parameters (admin only)
{command} (key=value ...)
*/{command}
show current AI configuration
*/{command} tokens=300
set max output tokens to 300
*/{command} model=/path/to/model.gguf
change model path
*/{command} binary=/path/to/llama-cli
change llama-cli binary path
*/{command} threads=4 timeout=120
set CPU threads and timeout